data.description: Explore comfort and convenience in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spanning 1,939 sq ft in Helena Park Addition. The classic layout includes a functional kitchen, spacious living areas, and three inviting bedrooms. Tasteful updates in the bathrooms blend modern convenience with timeless charm. With additional perks like extra parking and a shed, this home offers practicality and versatility.   Conveniently located near the elementary and middle schools, this home is a charming retreat with added amenities awaiting your personal touch. Schedule a tour today to discover the timeless appeal and possibilities this residence offers!
